kfritz (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Sound on incoming call (closes #7).
  * Phonebook/blocklist quick-actions: caller ID lookup and blocking now
    check multiple phonebooks per role, with one designated write target
    each so a WebDAV-synced blocklist can't get overwritten.
  * Missed calls from while the widget wasn't running are now caught up
    on startup via the FritzBox's own call list.
  * CMakeLists.txt no longer requires a giant unused KDE Workspace KCM
    dependency set; fixed a bug shipping raw plugin sources as data files.
  * Fixed "KKFritz" typo in metadata.json.

 -- Agundur <info@agundur.de>  Wed, 08 Jul 2026 14:00:00 +0200

